						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the temple of Bhaṇḍāridēva.</p>						

						<p>Mallikārjuna, 1455 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record refers to Liṅgappa-daṇāyaka and Bārakūru-rājya. All other details are lost.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 13[7]*7, (1378 current), <hi rend="bold">Yuva, Āśvija śu. 11, Sunday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1455 A.D., September 21.</hi></p>						

